snippet.title: VLORP (Coming Soon)
snippet.description:
Vlorp is a multiplayer hoverkart collector combat racing adventure game. 
Wishlist on steam- https://store.steampowered.com/app/1508420/VLORP/
To apply to beta test, visit the official website- vlorp.io
On itch- https://lemmyadam.itch.io/vlorp
Join the discord- https://discord.gg/2tc9Bz8wcS
